name: Ants Took My Eyeball (itch)
description:
You stumble at the wrong place at the wrong time and lose your eyeball. It's taken by ants deep into their nest.

Fight your way down the ant nest in your quest to get your eyeball back.

Made for the 34th gm(48) game jam in 48 hours.

Credits: dosto, henrimikael, Reaktori, Riuku.
